{"tid":563054,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"寫故寫你個名","createTime":"2018-02-16T13:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T13:32:47.000Z","uid":29132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"4ced00742c75083b36d7e3694c3e19e8e0d7a34a","tid":563054,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"無錯，入黎留言幫你個名寫個故仔，現家放假冇野做就寫下野啦。<br />\n我記得舊登之前有個叫賣帽人嘅巴打玩過類似嘅野，而我都好屎忽痕寫返個故仔比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然到最後好似未寫到我個名就消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   唔知有冇機會相應呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦都係佢令到我好想試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後亦係最重要個點，簡單嚟講，得閒嘅寫到就寫，我同我老母都唔會負上任何責任嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n附上送俾賣帽人巴打個篇故仔<br />\n<br />\n賣帽人<br />\n<br />\n我靜靜躺在玻璃箱內，看著眼前的男子把各式各樣的帽子推介給每一名走進店內的客人。可喜的是我看著朋友們找到良好的歸宿，可恨的是我卻一直安躺於玻璃櫃內。<br />\n<br />\n我的最好朋友是一頂土耳其毯帽，它居住在陳列櫃內，它常說：「作為一頂帽子，能夠找到適合自己的主人是最幸福的事。」<br />\n<br />\n「這位客人，我相信這頂土耳其毯帽是最適合你的。」眼前男子說道。<br />\n「我也是這樣認為。」一名自稱為博士的客人回應。<br />\n<br />\n就在這刻，我知道我最好的朋友即將離我而去，我為它能找到歸宿而快樂，這是它的期盼，誰也不能剝削它獲得幸福的權利。那麼我的幸福又在那兒？<br />\n<br />\n縱使店再次回復平靜，我對幸福的期盼卻從未終止，為何我生命的歸宿仍遲遲未來迎接我？我只能躺在玻璃櫃內寂靜地等待。<br />\n<br />\n日復日之，寂寥依然伴我。但今天卻有所不同，眼前的男子提早把店門關上，男子亦換上一身筆整的宴會禮服，感覺像是歡悅的時刻來臨。<br />\n<br />\n男子徐徐地站在我的眼前，當玻璃櫃被打開的時候，我終於明白我所尋找的早已在我的眼前，那種幸福原來一直都在，眼前的男子就是我的歸宿，那位賣帽人。"},{"pid":"5b599acb5d579a1309f7afa490ba96115f1e33a5","tid":563054,"uid":155180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打"},{"pid":"912747a65cfde2d73f0bdee49377af3f15ff2ee5","tid":563054,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff10efef56aea3f0bb7818627b366bac15bda9e","tid":563054,"uid":72693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9339f054ef6a29c11e07c6c4300bebcd1c2419fc","tid":563054,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ff10efef56aea3f0bb7818627b366bac15bda9e","tid":563054,"uid":72693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"達仔今晚開唔開台"},{"pid":"0b97b18a82cea0f6d000b46f8e96470dbddb9b99","tid":563054,"uid":103419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cde451dc1798cc7d2b9b7f43ef247d04e0ae9e","tid":563054,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b97b18a82cea0f6d000b46f8e96470dbddb9b99","tid":563054,"uid":103419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"達哥今晚開唔開枱"},{"pid":"5d373d1ec6a0ce8c52373aba3cc4956d43dbb5ad","tid":563054,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad22bc9efd431b5ecb6c0d7808ea8a5694688494","tid":563054,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d373d1ec6a0ce8c52373aba3cc4956d43dbb5ad","tid":563054,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"答下我想問下 達哥 今晚開唔開枱"},{"pid":"c1a658bc9e675821993f235b29757a9518b70318","tid":563054,"uid":92730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:55:15.000Z","msg":"留名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8640c5de0694f08157d8b9348a8c1b621408ae5a","tid":563054,"uid":70133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822708d8202351f680614c0f0965dae6c601a5f2","tid":563054,"uid":7741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce77afe116d361645af813e856f9514fba96a169","tid":563054,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"睇下你點寫先"},{"pid":"80f50d3bf43c8517b53329beece3dfda4e68c5f0","tid":563054,"uid":111751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:00:21.000Z","msg":"想睇"},{"pid":"fc52ca60b2ca46c1020ec791950597a463d6ec14","tid":563054,"uid":155354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"a9f50be3151129a22a7d5581ee39578706dfeec7","tid":563054,"uid":108910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:05:13.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff760a6d0dcd4ad6ad4e26fe4770150e0ed94b9","tid":563054,"uid":112950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db42bb624bb106bce57d29780cb75aa667c0f958","tid":563054,"uid":148266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8074904578ccc2552b6cbe9212c32759c1a827d5","tid":563054,"uid":155745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"留名睇故<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509940878b4e82b5cff7ae72c7dd9ca6f4577501","tid":563054,"uid":135196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"234367f8df63e0f558da746f08342b27937ec206","tid":563054,"uid":144784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4742f063df0f71844e447a72e06f983d187bfd41","tid":563054,"uid":148784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"發個大財樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f309c71e43eb890bbfa13d8e3710137759df2f","tid":563054,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:17:06.000Z","msg":"坦白講，之前睇人玩就幾有趣，原來到自己寫就好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  寫得差都唔知點面對好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3034174e19c1644bb49e7d969855c92f119cb553","tid":563054,"uid":155354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:41:05.000Z","msg":"試下無妨<br />\n寫完大家再討論下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b36e29bce03dbb2451a7347b5ab25b76d31025","tid":563054,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b599acb5d579a1309f7afa490ba96115f1e33a5","tid":563054,"uid":155180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"坦白講，睇到你個名第一眼就諗起鋼錬，所以我個腦唔知痴咗邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地球一粒塵<br />\n<br />\n我於此，我亦只知此。<br />\n我不知道自己從何而來，從我自知以來就身於這個寂靜的角落，我只見一切在變，而我卻未曾變。在我眼前的只有如常的景況，如常的離去，如常的歸來，日復如是。<br />\n<br />\n我於此，我亦只知此。<br />\n我不知道自己為何而生，從我自知以來就身於這個熱鬧的城市，我看見一切在變，我亦在變。在我眼前的是如常的面孔，如常的厭惡，而我亦如常的接受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我於此，我亦只知此。<br />\n我知道自己因何而在，我自知皆因萬物自知，我自知一切在變。如常的開採，如常的砍伐，如常的污染，而我如常的難以反抗。<br />\n<br />\n我們能不止於此，我們能不止於如常。<br />\n如常的是塵，如常的是人，如常的是地球。我是地球一粒塵，艾力克兄弟也是地球一粒塵，但我們能選擇不止於如常。"}]}